🔐 Current Security Controls

Password policy:
- Minimum 8 characters
- Password changes every 180 days

Access management:
- Developers have admin access in staging
- DevOps team has production access
- No formal quarterly access review

Backups:
- Automated AWS RDS daily backups
- No restore testing performed

Incident response:
- Informal Slack reporting
- No formal IR procedure

Vendor management:
- Vendors used: AWS, Stripe, SendGrid
- No formal vendor risk assessment

